From 7c1660f0b8df22757680df0b992b6ecd14f1ce5b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: lidslabs
Date: Mon, 15 Jun 2026 19:18:14 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] lidslabs HDR transcode patches
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Patches against jellyfin upstream — version pin lives in build repo, not
in this commit message, to avoid stale-subject confusion after rebases.

- HDR10/HDR10+/HLG passthrough for HEVC/AV1 encode (gated by JELLYFIN_ALLOW_HDR_TRANSCODE)
- DV Profile 7 conditional software decode when subtitle is engaged
- mainEndsInCudaMemory widening for sw-decoder + nvenc + HDR-passthrough subtitle burn-in
- Audio compatibility-track redirect
- HLS manifest tagging (VIDEO-RANGE=PQ/HLG, hvc1.2.4.* for Main10)
---
