 Jellyfin.Api/Helpers/DynamicHlsHelper.cs      |  25 +-
 .../MediaEncoding/EncodingHelper.cs           | 335 +++++++++++++++++-
 .../MediaEncoding/EncodingJobInfo.cs          |  17 +
 4 files changed, 405 insertions(+), 12 deletions(-)

